OL,6,FA Belfast man on trial for murdering
OL,7,Fhis wife was described as a "very
OL,8,Fgentle, very kind" man by the couple's
OL,9,Feldest child.JThe daughter of accused
OL,10,FGary Alexander Baird was called to
OL,11,Fgive evidence at Belfast Crown Court
OL,12,Fwhere she spoke of concerns regarding
OL,13,Fher father's mental health prior to
OL,14,Fthe fatal hammer attack.JBaird (64)
OL,15,Fhas already admitted attacking his 60-
OL,16,Fyear old wife Susan with a hammer and
OL,17,Fhas pleaded guilty to a charge of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter but this plea has not
OL,19,Fbeen accepted by the prosecution.
